project.title: Budget Tracker
project.about: A budget tracking application that works offline using the browser's indexedDB and a service worker to cache static files.

project.title: Burger Logger
project.about: A burger logging application that demonstrates the use of ORM utilization, MVC file structure, Handlebars, MySQL, Node, and Express

project.title: README Generator
project.about: A command line professional README generator. That uses Node, Inquirer and makes an axios call to get the badge of your choice.

project.title: Panda Patter
project.about: A team project that I worked on. I set up Firebase Authentication, the protect routes and used MongoDB, Express and React to render and save the flashcards.

project.title: React Employee Directory
project.about: An employee directory created with React. The Random User API returns 100 random users. They can be filtered by using the search bar or sorted by last name.

project.title: Hawk Box
project.about: A Seahawks fan forum. Make an account and post videos and comments. This was a group project that was made with Handlebars, passport, express and mySQL.
